To configure this software, follow these steps:
- edit configuration params in config.inc.php
- make foaf.rdf writable by the web server user
- update admin/.htaccess with correct authentication parameters

If installing from source repository, you'll also need to:
- apply patches to 3rd party libraries by running the following command:
 
    patch -p0 <patches/*.patch

  make sure patched files have the right permissions for your web server to use them
